A lightweight php MVC framework. This is a refactored version of code developed at Technorati.

here's a suggested http-conf:  

<VirtualHost *:80>
	# Add yoursite to your /etc/hosts file so you can
	# type it directly in your browser
	ServerName website.local
	ServerAdmin webmaster@website.com
	DocumentRoot /Library/WebServer/Documents/temovico/app/public
	
	RewriteEngine On
	RewriteRule ^/([^images|/js|/css]) /index.php
</VirtualHost>



